title: Top lane main Looking for a team. Needed for this weeks OOL
body:
Just played in the first round of the Throwdown qualifiers. Managed to match it against Challenger Player Abyss Papryze on my Fiora pick. 
Looking for a team diamond +. If interested contact me on the league of legends client. Username SeaguII. 
Thats two capital i's not l's.
